          "text": [
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "We’ve created digital resources to help teachers prepare for a self-directed visit to our permanent exhibitions, Medicine Man and Medicine Now. As Wellcome Collection is a venue that encourages visits from the incurably curious aged 14 and above, we’ve targeted these activities at students aged 14-19 years.",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "The resources include:",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "list-item",
              "content": {
                "text": "differentiated in-gallery activities that encourage students to engage with our fascinating collections in person",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "list-item",
              "content": {
                "text": "preparation and follow-up activities that can be completed back in the classroom",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "list-item",
              "content": {
                "text": "curriculum links and clear instructions on how to use these resources.",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Each resource has been split into separate PDFs so that you can download the section you need. Alternatively, you can also download all of each gallery’s resources in one PDF, which also includes a gallery plan.",
                "spans": []
              }
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "content": {
                "text": "Please also look at our Visiting Guidelines to ensure you get the most out of your visit:Visiting Guidelines (217 KB)",
                "spans": [
                  {
                    "start": 89,
                    "end": 89,
                    "data": {}
                  },
                  {
                    "start": 89,
                    "end": 89,
